<i> have faced off</i>
<i> in the ultimate competition...</i>

00:05.965 --> 00:07.965
- Getting pretty hot
in the kitchen.

00:08.009 --> 00:10.718
<i> - Making some of history's</i>
<i> deadliest weapons.</i>

00:10.761 --> 00:12.970
<i> Now, with the stakes</i>
<i> higher than ever,</i>

00:13.014 --> 00:14.930
<i> a new batch of bladesmiths</i>
<i> entered the Forge</i>

00:14.974 --> 00:16.473
<i> to test their skills.</i>

00:16.517 --> 00:19.518
- Whoa, whoa, watch out,
watch out, watch out.

00:19.562 --> 00:21.437
<i> - Only one will take home</i>
<i> $10,000...</i>

00:21.480 --> 00:23.230
- Whoo!

