- Oh, so that's how you set
the Forge weld on the hammer?

09:01.750 --> 09:03.708
- That's not
how I would do it.

09:03.752 --> 09:06.169
I would actually stand
in front of the hammer...

09:06.213 --> 09:08.046
- Yeah, me too.
- Not behind it.

09:08.090 --> 09:10.799
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

09:10.842 --> 09:12.759
- Andy has lost his handle.

09:12.803 --> 09:14.678
- I'm watching
Andy's body language.

09:14.721 --> 09:17.138
He's--he's freaking out
a little bit.

09:17.182 --> 09:18.306
- What the hell?

09:18.350 --> 09:23.353
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

09:23.397 --> 09:25.230
- [bleep].
- Whoa!

09:29.987 --> 09:33.363
<i> [dramatic music]</i>

09:33.407 --> 09:34.656
- Look at Shayne.

09:34.700 --> 09:35.782
- Cool.

