<i> ♪ ♪</i>

09:41.248 --> 09:42.497
- Whoa!
- Whoa, whoa, whoa!

09:42.541 --> 09:44.165
Watch out,
watch out, watch out.

09:44.209 --> 09:45.625
- What just happened?

09:45.669 --> 09:47.043
- [bleep] me.

09:47.087 --> 09:49.754
- We just almost had
a branding.

09:49.798 --> 09:51.506
Carry that metal down low

09:51.550 --> 09:53.508
and do not go running
across the floor.

09:53.552 --> 09:55.468
- Whew.

09:55.512 --> 09:57.387
- Oh, that ain't good.
I got a big-ass crack in it.

09:57.431 --> 10:00.473
That MIG weld in the middle
is starting to come apart.

10:00.517 --> 10:02.642
- Half of that is
basically useless.

10:02.686 --> 10:04.394
<i> - I'm just banking</i>
<i> on the fact</i>

10:04.438 --> 10:06.688
that one side of this will be
enough to make the blade.

10:06.732 --> 10:08.648
- Son of a bitch!

10:08.692 --> 10:10.150
<i> [dramatic music]</i>

10:10.193 --> 10:12.068
<i> - The blade I'm making,</i>
<i> a kopis,</i>

10:12.112 --> 10:14.738
<i> that's like the predecessor</i>
<i> to the falcata,</i>

10:14.781 --> 10:16.406
<i> and the falcata,</i>
<i> well, doesn't have</i>

10:16.450 --> 10:17.866
<i> the same kind</i>
<i> of handle details.</i>

