you weaken the grip.

10:30.172 --> 10:32.756
<i> [rock music]</i>

10:32.799 --> 10:35.467
- Aw, [bleep] balls.
Grinder kiss.

10:35.510 --> 10:37.385
I'm extremely accident prone.

10:37.429 --> 10:38.678
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

10:38.722 --> 10:41.431
Oh, you gotta be
freaking joking me.

10:41.475 --> 10:44.017
Aw, [bleep] balls!

10:44.061 --> 10:45.226
<i> Cut it down</i>
<i> into the cartilage.</i>

10:45.270 --> 10:48.229
I'm getting a bit
of the arthritis

10:48.273 --> 10:50.273
going on
here in this finger.

