14:26.241 --> 14:28.575
Your blade did not
make the cut.

14:28.618 --> 14:31.828
- Mike, sometimes abandon
a piece that's not working

14:31.872 --> 14:33.204
and change your direction.

14:33.248 --> 14:35.373
Your blade is under length,

