14:41.673 --> 14:43.756
<i> [rock music]</i>

14:43.800 --> 14:45.466
<i> - I'm obviously</i>
<i> a little disheartened</i>

14:45.510 --> 14:46.926
<i> to have been</i>
<i> eliminated.</i>

14:46.970 --> 14:48.845
It was
a great learning experience

14:48.889 --> 14:50.513
<i> of my own limitations</i>

14:50.557 --> 14:53.057
<i> and my own</i>
<i> damn "headstrongness."</i>

14:53.101 --> 14:54.809
<i> Now I'm gonna go home</i>
<i> and I'm gonna make</i>

14:54.853 --> 14:56.477
that suit of armor
so I can finally

14:56.521 --> 14:58.730
<i> get around</i>
<i> to the wedding.</i>

14:58.773 --> 15:00.481
<i> [dramatic music]</i>

