more interesting.

15:14.205 --> 15:16.831
You can only use
the recycled materials

15:16.875 --> 15:18.291
on that table
in front of the pantry

15:18.335 --> 15:20.919
to construct
your handles.

15:20.962 --> 15:22.837
<i> - My heart just sank.</i>

15:22.881 --> 15:24.547
<i> Here I've put all this effort</i>
<i> into this blade,</i>

15:24.591 --> 15:26.966
and I've got to use
inferior product on the handle.

15:27.010 --> 15:29.052
- Your finished weapons
will then be tested

15:29.095 --> 15:32.347
<i> in a bone marrow chop</i>
<i> and a sandbag slice.</i>

15:32.390 --> 15:34.474
You will have three hours
for this round.

