You can use that time to address
any flaws or issues

15:36.686 --> 15:38.186
that were identified
with your blades

15:38.229 --> 15:40.480
after the first round,
but keep in mind,

15:40.523 --> 15:43.816
when time runs out and
your weapons have been tested,

15:43.860 --> 15:46.611
one of you will
have to surrender his weapon

15:46.655 --> 15:48.363
and leave the Forge.

15:48.406 --> 15:51.074
Bladesmiths,
your time starts...

15:51.117 --> 15:52.116
now.

15:52.160 --> 15:54.077
<i> [rock music]</i>

15:54.120 --> 15:55.370
<i> - I'm the first one</i>
<i> at the table</i>

15:55.413 --> 15:56.996
<i> looking</i>
<i> for handle material,</i>

