so I thought,
"You know what,

15:58.375 --> 16:00.375
<i> rubber makes</i>
<i> a great handle."</i>

16:00.418 --> 16:03.086
- We do have
three sufficient blades

16:03.129 --> 16:05.046
going into this round.

