It could all come down
to the handle.

16:06.925 --> 16:08.716
- Yeah.

16:08.760 --> 16:11.052
<i> - So I find</i>
<i> a piece of furniture,</i>

16:11.096 --> 16:14.639
but the first thing I gotta do
is repair the issues

16:14.683 --> 16:18.226
