16:22.107 --> 16:24.190
- That guard
on that band saw blade

16:24.234 --> 16:26.192
should come down.

16:26.236 --> 16:28.152
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

16:28.196 --> 16:29.696
- Whoa!
- That'll make your heart skip.

16:29.739 --> 16:31.239
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

16:31.282 --> 16:32.490
<i> - I really need</i>
<i> to give the blade</i>

16:32.534 --> 16:34.492
<i> a little more attention.</i>

