- Underneath that sole
they're hollow.

17:03.690 --> 17:05.189
- He just found out
it's honeycomb.

17:05.233 --> 17:07.025
- Yeah.

17:07.068 --> 17:08.651
- Can you believe how cheap
these boots are made?

17:08.695 --> 17:09.694
There's a hole
right down the middle of 'em.

17:09.738 --> 17:12.405
<i> [rhythmic music]</i>

17:12.449 --> 17:16.325
- You have only 90 minutes
remaining to finish your work.

