- 15 minutes,
bladesmiths.

19:06.521 --> 19:09.689
You have 15 minutes remaining
to finish your work.

19:09.732 --> 19:12.608
- It ain't hardening up.

19:15.071 --> 19:17.405
- Oh, great.
