And, it's sharp.

36:53.670 --> 36:56.046
This, sir, will cut.
Good job.

36:56.089 --> 36:57.422
- Thank you.

36:57.466 --> 36:58.840
<i> [rock music]</i>

36:58.884 --> 37:01.176
- Bladesmiths,
