37:46.515 --> 37:49.349
This, sir, will kill.
Great job.

37:49.393 --> 37:50.475
- Thank you.

37:50.519 --> 37:52.519
- Andy, you're up next.
Ready?

37:52.562 --> 37:53.561
- Yes, sir.

37:53.605 --> 37:56.564
<i> [rock music]</i>

37:56.608 --> 38:02.237
