this dummy.

38:14.167 --> 38:16.251
This, sir, will kill.

38:16.295 --> 38:18.253
- Great job.
- Thank you.

38:18.297 --> 38:20.714
<i> [dramatic music]</i>

38:20.757 --> 38:23.300
- Gentlemen, your final test
