38:23.343 --> 38:26.052
The butterfly swords come
from southern China.

38:26.096 --> 38:27.762
Now, though they were used
by the military,

38:27.806 --> 38:30.223
primarily they're
a civilian weapon.

38:30.267 --> 38:31.891
Now, to test the strength
of your blades,

38:31.935 --> 38:34.436
I'm going to take six chops
into this ice block.

38:34.479 --> 38:36.938
